r: 0px; line-height: 22px; text-align: justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px;\\\"><span style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;\\\"><span style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\\\">Theo kh\\u1ea3o s\\u00e1t m\\u1edbi nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1ec1 c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c qu\\u1ea3n tr\\u1ecb c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u th\\u00ec m\\u1ee9c l\\u01b0\\u01a1ng dao \\u0111\\u1ed9ng trong kho\\u1ea3ng t\\u1eeb 7 - 15 tri\\u1ec7u\\/th\\u00e1ng d\\u00e0nh cho nh\\u1eefng b\\u1ea1n sinh vi\\u00ean m\\u1edbi ra tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u00e0 ch\\u01b0a c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1u kinh nghi\\u1ec7m l\\u00e0m vi\\u1ec7c. \\u0110\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c c\\u00f4ng ty l\\u1edbn v\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng nh\\u00e2n vi\\u00ean qu\\u1ea3n tr\\u1ecb c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u00e3 c\\u00f3 kinh nghi\\u1ec7m l\\u00e0m vi\\u1ec7c t\\u1ea1i v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed n\\u00e0y th\\u00ec m\\u1ee9c l\\u01b0\\u01a1ng h\\u1ecd \\u0111\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u1eeb 15 - 25 tri\\u1ec7u\\/th\\u00e1ng. T\\u1ea1i M\\u1ef9, thu nh\\u1eadp trung b\\u00ecnh cho trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c n\\u00e0y b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u1eeb 86.550 USD\\/n\\u0103m cho c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean vi\\u00ean v\\u00e0 l\\u00ean t\\u1edbi 146.360 USD\\/n\\u0103m cho c\\u00e1c nh\\u00e0 qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd m\\u00e1y t\\u00ednh v\\u00e0 h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng th\\u00f4ng tin.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><\\/article><\\/section><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div>\"', '[null,null,null]', 2, NULL, NULL);
