(2, 'Bài 2  RDBMS là gì?', '1702827231.png', '\"<div style=\\\"outline: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 17.3px;\\\"><h2 id=\\\"goto-h2-1\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.6rem; text-align: justify;\\\">RDBMS l\\u00e0 g\\u00ec?<\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">RDBMS l\\u00e0 vi\\u1ebft t\\u1eaft c\\u1ee7a Relational Database Management System c\\u00f3 ngh\\u0129a l\\u00e0 h\\u1ec7 qu\\u1ea3n tr\\u1ecb c\\u01a1 s\\u1ee1 d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u quan h\\u1ec7. RDBMS l\\u00e0 c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf cho SQL, v\\u00e0 cho t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i nh\\u01b0 MS SQL Server, IBM DB2, Oracle, MySQL v\\u00e0 Microsoft Access.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">H\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u quan h\\u1ec7 (RDBMS) l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u (DBMS) d\\u1ef1a tr\\u00ean m\\u00f4 h\\u00ecnh quan h\\u1ec7 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u b\\u1edfi EF Codd.<\\/p><h2 id=\\\"goto-h2-2\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.6rem; text-align: justify;\\\">B\\u1ea3ng l\\u00e0 g\\u00ec?<\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">D\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u trong m\\u1ed9t RDBMS \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u01b0u tr\\u1eef trong c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c g\\u1ecdi l\\u00e0&nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-weight: 700;\\\">c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea3ng (table)<\\/span>&nbsp;. B\\u1ea3ng n\\u00e0y v\\u1ec1 c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp c\\u00e1c m\\u1ee5c nh\\u1eadp d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u c\\u00f3 li\\u00ean quan v\\u00e0 n\\u00f3 bao g\\u1ed3m nhi\\u1ec1u c\\u1ed9t v\\u00e0 h\\u00e0ng.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">B\\u1ea3ng l\\u00e0 h\\u00ecnh th\\u1ee9c l\\u01b0u tr\\u1eef d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01a1n gi\\u1ea3n nh\\u1ea5t trong m\\u1ed9t c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u quan h\\u1ec7. Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh sau \\u0111\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t v\\u00ed d\\u1ee5 v\\u1ec1 m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ea3ng KHACH_HANG<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/viettuts.vn\\/sql\\/rdbms-la-gi#\\\" class=\\\"toolbar_item command_help help\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Bitstream Vera Sans Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; transition: all 0.1s ease-in-out 0s; font-size: 1em !important; box-sizing: content-box !important; color: white !important; border-radius: 0px !important; background-image: none !important; background-position: initial !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: initial !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; border: 0px !important; inset: auto !important; height: auto !important; line-height: 1.1em !important; margin: 0px !important; overflow: visible !important; padding: 1px 0px 0px !important; position: static !important; text-align: center !important; vertical-align: baseline !important; width: auto !important; direction: ltr !important; box-shadow: none !important; display: inline !important;\\\">?<\\/a><\\/p><h2 id=\\\"goto-h2-3\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.6rem; text-align: justify;\\\">Tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng l\\u00e0 g\\u00ec<\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">M\\u1ed7i b\\u1ea3ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c chia th\\u00e0nh c\\u00e1c th\\u1ef1c th\\u1ec3 nh\\u1ecf g\\u1ecdi l\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng. C\\u00e1c tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng trong b\\u1ea3ng KHACH_HANG bao g\\u1ed3m ID, TEN, TUOI, DIA_CHI V\\u00c0 LUONG.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">Tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t c\\u1ed9t trong m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ea3ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u01b0u tr\\u1eef th\\u00f4ng tin c\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3 v\\u1ec1 m\\u1ed7i b\\u1ea3n ghi trong b\\u1ea3ng.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\"><br><\\/p><h2 id=\\\"goto-h2-4\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.6rem; text-align: justify;\\\">B\\u1ea3n ghi ho\\u1eb7c m\\u1ed9t h\\u00e0ng (row) l\\u00e0 g\\u00ec?<\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">M\\u1ed9t b\\u1ea3n ghi c\\u0169ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c g\\u1ecdi l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t h\\u00e0ng d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u l\\u00e0 t\\u1eebng m\\u1ee5c ri\\u00eang l\\u1ebb t\\u1ed3n t\\u1ea1i trong m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ea3ng. V\\u00ed d\\u1ee5: c\\u00f3 3 b\\u1ea3n ghi trong b\\u1ea3ng KHACH_HANG tr\\u00ean. Sau \\u0111\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t h\\u00e0ng d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u ho\\u1eb7c m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ea3n ghi trong b\\u1ea3ng<\\/p><h2 id=\\\"goto-h2-5\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.6rem; text-align: justify;\\\">C\\u1ed9t (column) l\\u00e0 g\\u00ec?<\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">M\\u1ed9t c\\u1ed9t l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t th\\u1ef1c th\\u1ec3 th\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ee9ng trong m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ea3ng c\\u00f3 ch\\u1ee9a t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c th\\u00f4ng tin li\\u00ean k\\u1ebft v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9t tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3 trong m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ea3ng.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">V\\u00ed d\\u1ee5: m\\u1ed9t c\\u1ed9t trong b\\u1ea3ng KH\\u00c1CH H\\u00c0NG l\\u00e0 DIA_CHI, m\\u00f4 t\\u1ea3 v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed v\\u00e0 s\\u1ebd nh\\u01b0 d\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e2y:<\\/p><\\/div>\"', '[null,null,null]', 2, NULL, NULL),
