(9, 'Bài 3: Các hệ Quản trị CSDL', '1702827243.png', '\"<p><span style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">Hi\\u1ec7n nay, c\\u00f3 r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u RDBMS - h\\u1ec7 qu\\u1ea3n tr\\u1ecb c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn c\\u00f3 s\\u1eb5n \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u00e0m vi\\u1ec7c. H\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn n\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u01b0a ra m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1i nh\\u00ecn ng\\u1eafn g\\u1ecdn v\\u1ec1 m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 c\\u00e1c RDBMS ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn nh\\u1ea5t. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y s\\u1ebd gi\\u00fap b\\u1ea1n so s\\u00e1nh c\\u00e1c t\\u00ednh n\\u0103ng c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00fang.<\\/span><\\/p><h2 id=\\\"goto-h2-1\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.6rem; text-align: justify;\\\">MySQL<\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">MySQL l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t h\\u1ec7 qu\\u1ea3n tr\\u1ecb c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u SQL m\\u00e3 ngu\\u1ed3n m\\u1edf, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n b\\u1edfi m\\u1ed9t c\\u00f4ng ty Th\\u1ee5y \\u0110i\\u1ec3n - MySQL AB.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">MySQL h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng kh\\u00e1c nhau bao g\\u1ed3m Microsoft Windows, Linux, UNIX v\\u00e0 Mac OS X.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">MySQL c\\u00f3 c\\u00e1c phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n mi\\u1ec5n ph\\u00ed v\\u00e0 tr\\u1ea3 ph\\u00ed, t\\u00f9y thu\\u1ed9c v\\u00e0o c\\u00e1ch s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u1ee7a n\\u00f3 (phi th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i \\/ th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i) v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c t\\u00ednh n\\u0103ng. MySQL \\u0111i k\\u00e8m v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9t m\\u00e1y ch\\u1ee7 c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u SQL r\\u1ea5t nhanh, \\u0111a lu\\u1ed3ng, nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00f9ng v\\u00e0 m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd.<\\/p><h3 id=\\\"goto-h3-1\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.2rem; text-align: justify;\\\">L\\u1ecbch s\\u1eed<\\/h3><ul style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em 4rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\\"><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">S\\u1ef1 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n c\\u1ee7a MySQL b\\u1edfi Michael Widenius &amp; David Axmark b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u1eeb n\\u0103m 1994.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh n\\u1ed9i b\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean v\\u00e0o ng\\u00e0y 23&nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-size: 11.25px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\\\">th\\u1ee9<\\/span>&nbsp;Th\\u00e1ng n\\u0103m 1995.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n Windows \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh v\\u00e0o 8&nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-size: 11.25px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\\\">ng\\u00e0y<\\/span>&nbsp;th\\u00e1ng 1 n\\u0103m 1998 cho Windows 95 v\\u00e0 NT.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n 3,23: beta t\\u1eeb th\\u00e1ng 6 n\\u0103m 2000, s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t th\\u00e1ng 1\\/2001.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n 4.0: phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n beta t\\u1eeb th\\u00e1ng 8\\/2002, ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m th\\u00e1ng 3\\/2003 (c\\u00f4ng \\u0111o\\u00e0n).<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n 4.01: beta t\\u1eeb th\\u00e1ng 8 n\\u0103m 2003, Jyoti th\\u00f4ng qua MySQL \\u0111\\u1ec3 theo d\\u00f5i c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n 4.1: Phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n beta t\\u1eeb th\\u00e1ng 6 n\\u0103m 2004, s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t th\\u00e1ng 10 n\\u0103m 2004.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n 5.0: beta t\\u1eeb th\\u00e1ng 3 n\\u0103m 2005, ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m th\\u00e1ng 10 n\\u0103m 2005.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Sun Microsystems mua MySQL AB tr\\u00ean 26&nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-size: 11.25px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\\\">ng\\u00e0y<\\/span>&nbsp;th\\u00e1ng 2 n\\u0103m 2008.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Version 5.1: s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh 27&nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-size: 11.25px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\\\">ng\\u00e0y<\\/span>&nbsp;th\\u00e1ng 11 n\\u0103m 2008.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3 id=\\\"goto-h3-2\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.2rem; text-align: justify;\\\">T\\u00ednh n\\u0103ng, \\u0111\\u1eb7c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m<\\/h3><ul style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em 4rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\\"><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Hi\\u1ec7u su\\u1ea5t cao.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">T\\u00ednh s\\u1eb5n s\\u00e0ng cao.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng m\\u1edf r\\u1ed9ng v\\u00e0 T\\u00ednh linh ho\\u1ea1t Ch\\u1ea1y b\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee9 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u g\\u00ec.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">H\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 giao d\\u1ecbch m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">\\u0110i\\u1ec3m m\\u1ea1nh c\\u1ee7a Web v\\u00e0 Data Warehouse.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">B\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng to\\u00e0n di\\u1ec7n.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">T\\u1ef1 do ngu\\u1ed3n m\\u1edf v\\u00e0 H\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 24 x 7.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">T\\u1ed5ng chi ph\\u00ed s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu th\\u1ea5p nh\\u1ea5t.<\\/li><\\/ul><p><br style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\"><\\/p><h2 id=\\\"goto-h2-2\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.6rem; text-align: justify;\\\">MS SQL Server<\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">MS SQL Server l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t h\\u1ec7 qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u quan h\\u1ec7 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n b\\u1edfi Microsoft Inc Ng\\u00f4n ng\\u1eef truy v\\u1ea5n ch\\u00ednh c\\u1ee7a n\\u00f3 l\\u00e0:<\\/p><ul style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em 4rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\\"><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">T-SQL<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">ANSI SQL<\\/li><\\/ul><h3 id=\\\"goto-h3-3\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.2rem; text-align: justify;\\\">L\\u1ecbch s\\u1eed<\\/h3><ul style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em 4rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\\"><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">1987 - Sybase ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh SQL Server cho UNIX.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">1988 - Microsoft, Sybase, v\\u00e0 Aston-Tate c\\u1ed5ng SQL Server sang OS \\/ 2.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">1989 - Microsoft, Sybase, v\\u00e0 Aston-Tate ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh SQL Server 1.0 cho OS \\/ 2.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">1990 - SQL Server 1.1 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh v\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 cho kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng Windows 3.0.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Aston - Tate gi\\u1ecdt ra kh\\u1ecfi SQL Server ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">2000 - Microsoft ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh SQL Server 2000.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">2001 - Microsoft ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh XML cho SQL Server Web Release 1 (download).<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">2002 - Microsoft ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh SQLXML 2.0 (\\u0111\\u1ed5i t\\u00ean t\\u1eeb XML cho SQL Server).<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">2002 - Microsoft ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh SQLXML 3.0.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">2005 - Microsoft ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh SQL Server 2005 v\\u00e0o ng\\u00e0y 7 th\\u00e1ng 11 n\\u0103m 2005.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3 id=\\\"goto-h3-4\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.2rem; text-align: justify;\\\">T\\u00ednh n\\u0103ng, \\u0111\\u1eb7c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m<\\/h3><ul class=\\\"list\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em 4rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\\"><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Hi\\u1ec7u n\\u0103ng cao<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">T\\u00ednh s\\u1eb5n s\\u00e0ng cao<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Database mirroring<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Database snapshots<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">T\\u00edch CLR<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Service Broker<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">DDL triggers<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng Ranking<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Row version-based isolation levels<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">T\\u00edch h\\u1ee3p XML<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">TRY...CATCH - x\\u1eed l\\u00fd ngo\\u1ea1i l\\u1ec7<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Database Mail<\\/li><\\/ul><h2 id=\\\"goto-h2-3\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.6rem; text-align: justify;\\\">ORACLE<\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">\\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u \\u0111a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00f9ng r\\u1ea5t l\\u1edbn. Oracle l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t h\\u1ec7 qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u quan h\\u1ec7 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n b\\u1edfi \'T\\u1ed5ng c\\u00f4ng ty Oracle\'.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">Oracle l\\u00e0m vi\\u1ec7c \\u0111\\u1ec3 qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c ngu\\u1ed3n l\\u1ef1c, m\\u1ed9t c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u th\\u00f4ng tin gi\\u1eefa nhi\\u1ec1u kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u v\\u00e0 g\\u1eedi d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u trong m\\u1ea1ng.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">\\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn m\\u00e1y ch\\u1ee7 c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u tuy\\u1ec7t v\\u1eddi cho kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng \\/ m\\u00e1y t\\u00ednh m\\u00e1y t\\u00ednh. Oracle h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c h\\u1ec7 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u h\\u00e0nh ch\\u00ednh cho c\\u1ea3 kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0 m\\u00e1y ch\\u1ee7, bao g\\u1ed3m MSDOS, NetWare, UnixWare, OS \\/ 2 v\\u00e0 h\\u1ea7u h\\u1ebft c\\u00e1c h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v\\u1ecb UNIX.<\\/p><h3 id=\\\"goto-h3-5\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.2rem; text-align: justify;\\\">L\\u1ecbch s\\u1eed<\\/h3><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\">Oracle b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u v\\u00e0o n\\u0103m 1977 v\\u00e0 k\\u1ef7 ni\\u1ec7m 32 n\\u0103m tuy\\u1ec7t v\\u1eddi c\\u1ee7a n\\u00f3 trong ng\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p (t\\u1eeb n\\u0103m 1977 \\u0111\\u1ebfn n\\u0103m 2009).<\\/p><ul class=\\\"list\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em 4rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\\"><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">1977 - Larry Ellison, Bob Miner v\\u00e0 Ed Oates th\\u00e0nh l\\u1eadp c\\u00e1c Ph\\u00f2ng th\\u00ed nghi\\u1ec7m Ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n ph\\u1ea7n m\\u1ec1m \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea3m nh\\u1eadn c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">1979 - Phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n 2.0 c\\u1ee7a Oracle \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh v\\u00e0 tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u quan h\\u1ec7 th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean v\\u00e0 c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u SQL \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean.&nbsp;C\\u00f4ng ty \\u0111\\u1ed5i t\\u00ean th\\u00e0nh Relational Software Inc. (RSI).<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">1981 - RSI b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n c\\u00e1c c\\u00f4ng c\\u1ee5 cho Oracle.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">1982 - RSI \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u1ed5i t\\u00ean th\\u00e0nh T\\u1ed5ng c\\u00f4ng ty Oracle.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">1983 - Oracle ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n 3.0, vi\\u1ebft l\\u1ea1i b\\u1eb1ng ng\\u00f4n ng\\u1eef C v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ea1y tr\\u00ean nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">1984 - Oracle phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n 4.0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh.&nbsp;N\\u00f3 ch\\u1ee9a c\\u00e1c t\\u00ednh n\\u0103ng nh\\u01b0 ki\\u1ec3m so\\u00e1t \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi - s\\u1ef1 nh\\u1ea5t qu\\u00e1n \\u0111\\u1ecdc nhi\\u1ec1u phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n, v.v ...<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">1985 - Oracle phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n 4.0 \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh.&nbsp;N\\u00f3 ch\\u1ee9a c\\u00e1c t\\u00ednh n\\u0103ng nh\\u01b0 ki\\u1ec3m so\\u00e1t \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi - t\\u00ednh nh\\u1ea5t qu\\u00e1n \\u0111\\u1ecdc nhi\\u1ec1u phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n, v.v ...<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">2007 - Oracle ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh Oracle11g.&nbsp;Phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n m\\u1edbi t\\u1eadp trung v\\u00e0o ph\\u00e2n v\\u00f9ng t\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n, di chuy\\u1ec3n d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng, v.v.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3 id=\\\"goto-h3-6\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.2rem;\\\">T\\u00ednh n\\u0103ng, \\u0111\\u1eb7c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m<\\/h3><ul class=\\\"list\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em 4rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px;\\\"><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Truy c\\u1eadp \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">\\u0110\\u1ecdc t\\u00ednh nh\\u1ea5t qu\\u00e1n<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">C\\u01a1 ch\\u1ebf kh\\u00f3a<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">C\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u Quiesce<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">T\\u00ednh kh\\u1ea3 chuy\\u1ec3n<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">C\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u t\\u1ef1 qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">SQL*Plus<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">ASM<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Scheduler<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd T\\u00e0i nguy\\u00ean<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Data Warehousing<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Materialized views<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Bitmap indexes<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Table compression<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Th\\u1ef1c thi song song<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Ph\\u00e2n t\\u00edch SQL<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Data mining<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Partitioning<\\/li><\\/ul><p><font style=\\\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\\\"><br><\\/font><\\/p><h2 id=\\\"goto-h2-4\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.6rem;\\\">MS ACCESS<\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px;\\\">\\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a Microsoft. Microsoft Access l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t ph\\u1ea7n m\\u1ec1m qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u c\\u1ea5p c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf. C\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u MS Access kh\\u00f4ng ch\\u1ec9 l\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng t\\u1ed1n k\\u00e9m m\\u00e0 c\\u00f2n l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd cho c\\u00e1c d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n quy m\\u00f4 nh\\u1ecf.<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px;\\\">MS Access s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00f4ng c\\u1ee5 c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u Jet, s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng m\\u1ed9t ng\\u00f4n ng\\u1eef c\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3 ng\\u00f4n ng\\u1eef SQL (\\u0111\\u00f4i khi \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c g\\u1ecdi l\\u00e0 Jet SQL).<\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em; padding: 0px;\\\">MS Access \\u0111i k\\u00e8m v\\u1edbi phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n chuy\\u00ean nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u1ee7a g\\u00f3i MS Office. MS Access c\\u00f3 giao di\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ed3 h\\u1ecda tr\\u1ef1c quan s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng easyto.<\\/p><ul class=\\\"list\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em 4rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px;\\\"><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">1992 - Truy c\\u1eadp phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n 1.0 \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">1993 - Truy c\\u1eadp 1.1 ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng th\\u00edch v\\u1edbi vi\\u1ec7c bao g\\u1ed3m ng\\u00f4n ng\\u1eef l\\u1eadp tr\\u00ecnh Access Basic.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i quan tr\\u1ecdng nh\\u1ea5t l\\u00e0 t\\u1eeb Access 97 \\u0111\\u1ebfn Access 2000.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">2007 - Access 2007, m\\u1ed9t \\u0111\\u1ecbnh d\\u1ea1ng c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u m\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u ACCDB h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 c\\u00e1c ki\\u1ec3u d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u ph\\u1ee9c t\\u1ea1p nh\\u01b0 nhi\\u1ec1u l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c c\\u00f3 gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u00ednh k\\u00e8m.<\\/li><\\/ul><h3 id=\\\"goto-h3-7\\\" style=\\\"color: rgb(36, 76, 95); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.2rem;\\\">T\\u00ednh n\\u0103ng, \\u0111\\u1eb7c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m<\\/h3><ul class=\\\"list\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0em 0.2em 1em 4rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: justify;\\\"><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00f9ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o b\\u1ea3ng bi\\u1ec3u, truy v\\u1ea5n, bi\\u1ec3u m\\u1eabu v\\u00e0 b\\u00e1o c\\u00e1o v\\u00e0 k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i ch\\u00fang c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi macro.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">T\\u00f9y ch\\u1ecdn nh\\u1eadp v\\u00e0 xu\\u1ea5t d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u sang nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u1ecbnh d\\u1ea1ng bao g\\u1ed3m Excel, Outlook, ASCII, dBase, Paradox, FoxPro, SQL Server, Oracle, ODBC ...<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">C\\u0169ng c\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ecbnh d\\u1ea1ng Jet Database (MDB ho\\u1eb7c ACCDB trong Access 2007), c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ee9a \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e0 d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u trong m\\u1ed9t t\\u1ec7p.&nbsp;\\u0110i\\u1ec1u n\\u00e0y l\\u00e0m cho n\\u00f3 r\\u1ea5t thu\\u1eadn ti\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ec3 ph\\u00e2n ph\\u1ed1i to\\u00e0n b\\u1ed9 \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng cho ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00f9ng kh\\u00e1c, nh\\u1eefng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ea1y n\\u00f3 trong m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng b\\u1ecb ng\\u1eaft k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Microsoft Access cung c\\u1ea5p truy v\\u1ea5n tham s\\u1ed1.&nbsp;Nh\\u1eefng truy v\\u1ea5n v\\u00e0 b\\u1ea3ng truy c\\u1eadp c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tham chi\\u1ebfu t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh kh\\u00e1c nh\\u01b0 VB6 v\\u00e0. NET th\\u00f4ng qua DAO ho\\u1eb7c ADO.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">C\\u00e1c phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n m\\u00e1y t\\u00ednh \\u0111\\u1ec3 b\\u00e0n c\\u1ee7a Microsoft SQL Server c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng v\\u1edbi Access nh\\u01b0 l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ef1 thay th\\u1ebf cho Jet Database Engine.<\\/li><li style=\\\"list-style-type: disc;\\\">Microsoft Access l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u d\\u1ef1a tr\\u00ean m\\u00e1y ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1eadp tin.&nbsp;Kh\\u00f4ng gi\\u1ed1ng nh\\u01b0 c\\u00e1c h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u quan h\\u1ec7 kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng (RDBMS), Microsoft Access kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n c\\u00e1c tr\\u00ecnh kh\\u1edfi t\\u1ea1o c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u, c\\u00e1c th\\u1ee7 t\\u1ee5c l\\u01b0u tr\\u1eef ho\\u1eb7c \\u0111\\u0103ng nh\\u1eadp giao d\\u1ecbch.<\\/li><\\/ul><p><font style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\\\"><\\/font><br><\\/p>\"', '[null,null,null]', 2, NULL, NULL);
