p: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\\\">Collection l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t nh\\u00f3m c\\u00e1c Document trong MongoDB. N\\u00f3 t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng nh\\u01b0 m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ea3ng trong RDBMS. Do \\u0111\\u00f3, m\\u1ed9t Collection t\\u1ed3n t\\u1ea1i b\\u00ean trong m\\u1ed9t c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u duy nh\\u1ea5t. C\\u00e1c Collection kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 r\\u00e0ng bu\\u1ed9c Relationship nh\\u01b0 c\\u00e1c h\\u1ec7 qu\\u1ea3n tr\\u1ecb c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u kh\\u00e1c n\\u00ean vi\\u1ec7c truy xu\\u1ea5t r\\u1ea5t nhanh, ch\\u00ednh v\\u00ec th\\u1ebf m\\u1ed7i collection c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ee9a nhi\\u1ec1u th\\u1ec3 lo\\u1ea1i kh\\u00e1c nhau kh\\u00f4ng gi\\u1ed1ng nh\\u01b0 table trong h\\u1ec7 qu\\u1ea3n tr\\u1ecb mysql l\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c field c\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u1ecbnh. C\\u00e1c Document b\\u00ean trong m\\u1ed9t Collection c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1u tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng kh\\u00e1c nhau. \\u0110\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t, t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c Document trong m\\u1ed9t Collection l\\u00e0 t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u1ef1 nhau ho\\u1eb7c v\\u1edbi c\\u00f9ng m\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u00edch li\\u00ean quan.<\\/p><h2 style=\\\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -1px; margin-top: 20px; margin-right: 0.2em; line-height: 28px; text-shadow: none; font-size: 22px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; position: relative; left: 0px;\\\">Kh\\u00e1i ni\\u1ec7m Document<\\/h2><p style=\\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 24px; margin-right: 0.2em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0.2em; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\\\">M\\u1ed9t Document trong MongoDB, c\\u00f3 c\\u1ea5u tr\\u00fac t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u1ef1 nh\\u01b0 ki\\u1ec3u d\\u1eef li\\u1ec7u JSON, l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t 